income stream (Vesta).\",\"version\":1},\"userdoc\":{\"kind\":\"user\",\"methods\":{\"claim()\":{\"notice\":\"Pulls accrued benefit up to the current time (or death ts).\"}},\"notice\":\"For each retiree we store an annual benefit rate. Accrual is         linear in time while the retiree is alive (mortality oracle view).         Retirees pull by calling `claim()`.             accrual(t) = annualBenefit * (t - lastClaim) / SECONDS_PER_YEAR         Actual transfer happens by the streamer pulling from a funded         balance (filled by VestaRouter). On confirmed death the stream         freezes at the death timestamp.\",\"version\":1}},\"settings\":{\"compilationTarget\":{\"src/BenefitStreamer.sol\":\"BenefitStreamer\"},\"evmVersion\":\"paris\",\"libraries\":{},\"metadata\":{\"bytecodeHash\":\"ipfs\"},\"optimizer\":{\"enabled\":true,\"runs\":200},\"remappings\":[\":forge-std/=lib/forge-std/src/\"],\"viaIR\":true},\"sources\":{\"src/BenefitStreamer.sol\":{\"keccak256\":\"0xd4a00033db4ffe5193dd6f1870697326edb51c0b175809f848655b2571e5ce5e\",\"license\":\"MIT\",\"urls\":[\"bzz-raw://8612300babc960add5081c686acd68a39b57ce04fd0c5d5e5a6dd646abf2258b\",\"dweb:/ipfs/QmeqUh4MnsUwbCqzot1SvkiNo7USovu8HDhQPEiaN5ADgr\"]},\"src/interfaces/IMortalityOracle.sol\":{\"keccak256\":\"0xa004ab554142ca6f8a3742d183548224248e5b6a5299b71354ff1994b047cb8c\",\"license\":\"MIT\",\"urls\":[\"bzz-raw://bfb0c02016eb913b9f753fa6b2fdcd83ce2b04f9261dad35c74e96650a4705f5\",\"dweb:/ipfs/QmXyAt89H8175ytbh3JkFQgRJdNb8BV11fF4GxccMZE374\"]},\"src/utils/Owned.sol\":{\"keccak256\":\"0x2109ff61a043c0743eb8655c47b684c453657be35a41b4f35944156463678d48\",\"license\":\"MIT\",\"urls\":[\"bzz-raw://8be6ddcfcca1103fb7d748b68086d54946e6a087da2c2d758d5297192b968f0b\",\"dweb:/ipfs/Qme1HdBF1vT81ntD8PNT9dgy5JAQmSAKmvgjUufyr9YKf7\"]},\"src/utils/Roles.sol\":{\"keccak256\":\"0x2aa94822867486267b9c09f71bbd7f53111c0f1a764a9c55f19cd0b37c26d0ba\",\"license\":\"MIT\",\"urls\":[\"bzz-raw://16a78e21e63a0ebee01d538d28dc66ef559876ac9